{"tid":119543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男訂花送三女伴　中女自費買花扮收花","createTime":"2017-02-13T23:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T01:08:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db65b961f0f7978e65979428d8815ad266144579","tid":119543,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"每逢2月14日情人節，都是男士買花送給摯愛的日子，有花店店東細說多年來見盡的光怪陸離。曾有男顧客一次過訂購三束鮮花送給不同女伴；亦有為數不少的三十多歲中女提前在情人節前夕訂花，送貨地址雖為辦公室，但收貨人竟與送花者同名同姓，目的是送到自己公司「扮有花收」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/384142/xlarge/9e4835cf6f523a4c711f3d3ed8b6c5ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F384142%2Fxlarge%2F9e4835cf6f523a4c711f3d3ed8b6c5ce.jpg&h=97810c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n花店負責人梁小姐指，今個情人節適逢工作日，男士會要求送花予女友公司「曬命」，預料銷情比去年同期高一倍。（梁煥敏攝）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>花店遇「花心客」　送三束予不同女伴</strong><br />\n<br />\n說起情人節送花趣事，旺角花墟卉豐花業負責人梁小姐說，最深刻為曾有男士一次過訂三束鮮花，送給不同的女伴：「那位男士買的花是送去不同公司，又不同區，我們都感到愕然。」除了「花心男」，梁說近年多了三十多歲的中女到花店提前訂花，至正日送去公司，惟交錢落單時發現「送花和收花者為同一人」：「之前會覺得她們很慘，因為看外貌，她們似是有一定地位的女士，會覺得她們毋須這樣對自己，不過見多了就習慣。」<br />\n<br />\n她又說，同性戀者對買花尤為認真：「不論男女到花店揀花，都話細心挑選大半日，並且會買特別玫瑰花束，如田園玫瑰等，職員幫忙整理花束時也格外小心。」至於異性戀的男士，買花大多早有預算，為「速戰速決」絕不猶豫，「他們通常直接說預了多少錢，如一千元左右，我們就知大約是哪個級數的花。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/389935/xlarge/3eeb3fdca687ee869150582e8a8f3fbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F389935%2Fxlarge%2F3eeb3fdca687ee869150582e8a8f3fbd.jpg&h=7cb98aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n花店店主指，每年情人節均有數名中女為自己訂玫瑰花，並於正日送至自己公司「扮收花」。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>業界：今年訂單多逾一倍</strong><br />\n<br />\n梁小姐表示，去年情人節「撞正」農曆新年，前年卻是周末，而今年情人節適逢工作日，「正好給男士機會，買花送到女友公司『曬命』，否則女友會嬲！」她預料今年銷情按年高一倍，目前已收到過百宗訂單。價錢方面，梁小姐表示大部份男士會選擇1,000元至1,500元（價錢包括運送）花束，仍以傳統玫瑰花為首選。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓劇《鬼怪》熱推棉花　花束成熱賣貨</strong><br />\n<br />\n受熱播韓劇《孤單又燦爛的神 鬼怪》影響，梁小姐指，劇中男主角給女主角送贈的棉花花束，亦吸引一眾OL追棒，惟產自荷蘭的棉花當造期為每年12月，現時貨源短缺，「我們之前預訂，現時才有少量貨出售，但都少之又少。」680元的棉花花束，配合玫瑰乾花、滿天星等，可擺放最少兩個月，深得不少顧客喜愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/386397/xlarge/bcf30f02f52b8c53a540eb576cbf9195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F386397%2Fxlarge%2Fbcf30f02f52b8c53a540eb576cbf9195.jpg&h=3c5bfb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大熱韓劇《鬼怪》深受OL歡迎，不少港男亦仿傚劇中男主角送棉花表達愛意，惟產自荷蘭的棉花收成期已過，市面一花難求，三枝棉花加上襯花盛惠680元。（左：網上圖片/ 右：梁煥敏攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/386395/xlarge/ec5d6cb91073fa80abc5091150d6ca6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F386395%2Fxlarge%2Fec5d6cb91073fa80abc5091150d6ca6b.jpg&h=f85f2499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情人節將至，玫瑰花仍是大眾首選花束。（梁煥敏攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/71181/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C-%E8%8A%B1%E5%BA%97%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E8%A8%82%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%81%E4%B8%89%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A5%B3%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E8%B2%B7%E8%8A%B1%E6%89%AE%E6%94%B6%E8%8A%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F71181%2F-%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%2582%25B2%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259D%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%258A%25B1%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BC%25B4-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%2589%25AE%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%258A%25B1&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq45WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a6a8975e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/71181/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C-%E8%8A%B1%E5%BA%97%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E8%A8%82%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%81%E4%B8%89%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A5%B3%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E8%B2%B7%E8%8A%B1%E6%89%AE%E6%94%B6%E8%8A%B1</a>"},{"pid":"273da069d2229d30b34799eefaa5aa8f8c6bf57d","tid":119543,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:51:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">花店遇「花心客」　送三束予不同女伴<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n通常花店都會撈亂啲卡"},{"pid":"c1b6b31d3050790cde7d9d76ff9ed7629393af39","tid":119543,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:52:10.000Z","msg":"亦有為數不少的三十多歲中女提前在情人節前夕訂花，送貨地址雖為辦公室，但收貨人竟與送花者同名同姓，目的是送到自己公司「扮有花收」。<br />\n<br />\n真係陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb74cf6f4b346038466ff098bac7a40f18019a1d","tid":119543,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14d2c480ebf6ba64de4e92074933bdd7c3b000a","tid":119543,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:13:54.000Z","msg":"送棉花咁on9<br />\n幾時送返劍蘭"},{"pid":"04f725a5c8139dcfb011c63b4f27314dd60bf074","tid":119543,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:17:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822721152f3ac81ff5b333e9fb188ae32ada81e4","tid":119543,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩，咁樣唱d客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bcf08e221ed71c6f7fdebe84a1a99f461b9a59","tid":119543,"uid":30244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"送花員: 你訂嘅花已經送到，請簽收。"},{"pid":"b3022fd33b435bd83c579f33ae641700b3fc592a","tid":119543,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送花員: 你訂嘅花已經送到，請簽收。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n送花仔應該唔知邊個落訂掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78a34070816b0928df2e6c5d2d31c84fe3b5d22","tid":119543,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送棉花咁on9<br />\n幾時送返劍蘭</blockquote><br />\n紅棉盛~放，天氣暖洋洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英姿勃發堪~景~仰<br />\n英雄樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n力爭向上，志氣<span style=\"font-size: large;\">誰</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">能</span>~<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">擋</span>？"}]}